==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*γραμματεύς / grammateus / gram-mat-yooce'

===Etymology===
From [[γράμμα]] {{GG|1121}}; a writer, that is, (professionally) scribe or secretary:

===Noun===
'''γραμματεύς'''

# [[scribe]], town-clerk.

